  "detailed_description": "<h1>Also recommended for you</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581740/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.poster.avif?t=1626825669\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581740/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.webm?t=1626825669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581740/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.mp4?t=1626825669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581740/extras/ef63e988c18d4dce3a0b7df3a13d0a73.poster.avif?t=1626825669\" width=480 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581740/extras/ef63e988c18d4dce3a0b7df3a13d0a73.webm?t=1626825669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581740/extras/ef63e988c18d4dce3a0b7df3a13d0a73.mp4?t=1626825669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong> Do you know who was the first woman to go to space? What about the first animal? Don't panic! Laika will guide you through these discoveries and many more! </strong><br><br>Kosmo Laika: Guide to Space is a puzzle game of curiosities about space. You will be challenged to test your knowledge, <strong>combine exclusive patches to find the first visionaries in space, meet the \"animalnauts\" and conquerors of the Moon.</strong>  In this game, Laika will be your guide, taking you into space and beyond, like you never imagined.<br><br><strong>Featuring: </strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>70 different patches to combine and discover historical facts and important moments of the space missions; <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581740/extras/7dce2b687161d695613cf2c65de6f1c9.poster.avif?t=1626825669\" width=480 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581740/extras/7dce2b687161d695613cf2c65de6f1c9.webm?t=1626825669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581740/extras/7dce2b687161d695613cf2c65de6f1c9.mp4?t=1626825669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Complete over 25 moments of the space race; <br><br></li><li>Drag and drop the patches in the right places and complete the mission; <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581740/extras/404811150b3556607bd005c727bc0750.poster.avif?t=1626825669\" width=480 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581740/extras/404811150b3556607bd005c727bc0750.webm?t=1626825669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581740/extras/404811150b3556607bd005c727bc0750.mp4?t=1626825669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Earn exclusive stamps; <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581740/extras/6d44fbf79bcf36eca981895c7886ffce.poster.avif?t=1626825669\" width=480 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581740/extras/6d44fbf79bcf36eca981895c7886ffce.webm?t=1626825669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581740/extras/6d44fbf79bcf36eca981895c7886ffce.mp4?t=1626825669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Increase your knowledge of the history of astronomy; <br><br></li><li>Learn all about space heroes; <br><br></li><li>Meet the first animalnauts  of the missions. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581740/extras/23a400b440ff153d9d51d7000a5bf4e4.poster.avif?t=1626825669\" width=480 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581740/extras/23a400b440ff153d9d51d7000a5bf4e4.webm?t=1626825669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581740/extras/23a400b440ff153d9d51d7000a5bf4e4.mp4?t=1626825669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Great soundtrack. Original sound effects designed exclusively for the best experience. </li></ul><br>Test your knowledge of space exploration and the achievements that are part of the history of the world, with the help of Laika, the first space astronaut puppy. <br><br><i>For all lovers of trivia and puzzle games and who admire the stars!</i>",
